race.comment: HARDPOINT (2) collared late by the handy Master Of The Air two-back, before knocking up from the outside draw when ninth over 1600m at Kembla Grange. Strips fitter from the better gate with the claim. INVASIVE DREAMS (5) racing well in stronger contests and backs-up quickly after running a tough fourth over 1600m at Gosford from the outside gate. Will push forward from the low draw and gets her chance. HIBIKI HARMONY (3) gone to a new level this prep and deserves her chance here. Taken straight to the front and never headed when a dominant winner over 1500m at Muswellbrook. Winning apprentice sticks and comes here in peak condition. UNREAL EXPECTATION (6) has form at the trip and gripped on late when fifth over 1500m at Newcastle. Map looks tricky and place best. AFFERMATO (1) just over three-weeks between runs when a fading eighth over 2000m at Hawkesbury. Capable of better.
